<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<html xmlns:MadCap="http://www.madcapsoftware.com/Schemas/MadCap.xsd">
    <body>
        <ol>
            <li>In the XML Editor, find a question section where you want to add feedback.</li>
            <li>
                <span class="topic-only">Do one of the following, depending on the part of the user interface you are using:</span>
                <span class="micro-content-only">Select the <span class="Emphasis">eLearning</span> ribbon, and click the <span class="Emphasis">Add Feedback</span> button.</span>
                <ul class="topic-only">
                    <li>
                        <span class="Emphasis">Ribbon </span>From the <span class="Emphasis">eLearning</span> ribbon, select <span class="Emphasis">Add Feedback</span>.<p><img src="../../../Images/Flare/Interface/Buttons/LMS-Add-Feedback-btn.png" alt="" title="" /></p></li>
                    <li>
                        <p>
                            <span class="Emphasis">Right-Click </span>From the structure bar, right-click a question section tag, and then select <span class="Emphasis">Add Feedback</span>.</p>
                        <p>
                            <img src="../../../Images/Flare/LMS/LMS-Add-Feedback-Right-Click.png" alt="" title="" class="MaxWidth100Percent" />
                        </p>
                    </li>
                </ul>
                <p class="topic-only">Placeholder text relating to the corresponding question section tag gets inserted into the topic.</p>
            </li>
            <li>Replace the text with appropriate feedback material for the answer(s).</li>
            <li>
                <span class="micro-content-only">To add feedback for instant review, click <span class="Emphasis">Add Submit Button</span>.</span>
                <span class="topic-only">To add feedback for instant review, click <span class="Emphasis">Add Submit Button</span>. This adds a placeholder button. Do one of the following:</span>
                <ul class="topic-only">
                    <li>
                        <span class="Emphasis">Ribbon </span>From the <span class="Emphasis">eLearning</span> ribbon, select the <span class="Emphasis">Add Submit Button</span>.<p class="topic-only"><img src="../../../Images/Flare/Interface/Buttons/LMS-Add-Submit-btn.png" alt="" title="" /></p></li>
                    <li>
                        <p class="topic-only">
                            <span class="Emphasis">Right- Click</span> From the structure bar, right-click  a section question tag, and then select <span class="Emphasis">Add Submit Button</span>.</p>
                        <p class="topic-only">
                            <img src="../../../Images/Flare/LMS/LMS-Add-Submit-Button-Right-Click.png" alt="" title="" class="MaxWidth100Percent" />
                        </p>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </li>
            <li>
                <MadCap:snippetText src="../../Shared/All/General/Save-File.flsnp" />
            </li>
        </ol>
    </body>
</html>